scene.message:
Nanjo: Is no one home?{wait_fr:32}{nl}
...My, what a cozy little{nl}
house this is.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Well, compared to your{nl}
house, anywhere'd look like{nl}
a cozy little place!{waitkey}{clearbox}Honestly... this is just how{nl}
rich boys are...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: This is Yuko Himeno's{nl}
place, Sonomura's friend...{waitkey}{clearbox}I work a job for my own{nl}
future, but she does it for{nl}
her family's sake...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Nanjo, you oughta get a{nl}
job too and pay Yamaoka's{nl}
wages yourself!{waitkey}{ret}
